transcripts.text: Alma Mater, we hail thee with loyal devotion, and bring to thine altar our offerings of praise.  Our hearts swell within us with joyful emotion, As the name of Old Brown.  in loud chorus we raise, the happiest moments of youth.  has seen the shade of these time-honored walls and sorrows.  as transient as April's brief showers have clouded our lives in Brunonia's halls.
